==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun|sg=[[popular]] [[music]]|-}}

#{{music}} Any [[genre]] of [[music]] that has a wide appeal amongst the [[general public]] of a [[society]] dominated by [[urban]] [[culture]] and advanced [[technology]], especially music considered to have a lower [[value]] and [[complexity]] than "[[classical music]]"

